replies.body:
I just tried a bunch of stuff to solve it, but then I noticed that it was almost on a timer the 3-6 seconds of freezing in-game. 
{{champion:34}}  

My Solution: Window 10 Background was set to change every so often. Even though my comp is really good. League did not like it when my whole background and theme settings would change while playing. I stopped the background from being in slideshow and I have not had any freezing issue. 
{{item:3139}}
